Then bring Más Agave Premium Hard Seltzer home to admire for yourself by heading to our beer finder at the link in our bio.

Our education team is saddened they can’t host all of you for their famous brewery tours. So, we decided to do the next best thing and start a weekly beer education video series. Starting today, we’ll be releasing weekly beer education videos to help you pass the time and hopefully, help you come out of this with some new beer knowledge.

It's never too early to think about how you'll be spending your weekend! Let us help with a recipe that's good for breakfast or happy hour – Beergarita style. ⁠
⁠
All you need to do is salt your rim, throw in some ice and add: ⁠
⁠
-A shot of tequila⁠
-A shot of orange juice⁠
-A splash of lime juice⁠
-Top off with Unraveled IPA⁠
⁠
You can doctor this cocktail up however you want. In fact, throw in some suggestions in the comments! #foundersbrewing

On September 11 and 12, we’re bringing our #CraftedinMI series to life by debuting a Crafted in Michigan Market presented by @sixwaysmarkets at our Grand Rapids taproom!
 
This FREE, all-ages outdoor artist market will take place in our parking lot (on the corner of Wealthy and Grandville) and feature a variety of crafters and makers. We’ll also have special food offerings, roaming music by @nicholasjamesthomasma and lots of refreshing beer (obviously).
 
Expect to see vendors like @arsenalhandicraft, @happypeoplehike, @plutomonday, @anycolour_you_like, @beesinthed, @losttimberwoodwork and many more, so mark your calendars for September 11 & 12 for a weekend full of Michigan made art! More info at the link in bio. #foundersbrewing

Listen up all you KBS connoisseurs!⁠
⁠
Today’s the day that KBS Cinnamon Vanilla Cocoa, KBS Espresso and Nitro KBS all hit our taprooms in a delicious, chocolatey, barrel-aged fashion. Let’s take a second to talk about the new kid on the block. KBS Cinnamon Vanilla Cocoa incorporates a swirl of cinnamon and a hint of vanilla to create a sweet-but-not-too-sweet, full bodied sipper that clocks in at 12% ABV. This newbie is accompanied by the return of the familiar favorite, KBS Espresso, and the draft-only Nitro KBS.⁠
⁠
All three are now on draft in our taprooms, along with 4-packs of KBS Espresso and KBS Cinnamon Vanilla Cocoa. The rest of you will begin to see them in your neck of the woods in October. #foundersbrewing

node.text:
We’re bringing back a favorite to our Brewed for MI Series, and you’re going to love it. We promise.⁠
⁠
That’s right, Mosaic Promise is coming back to the mitten! Coming in at 5.5% ABV, this Single Hopped Ale showcases Mosaic hops and Golden Promise malt to create a clean, rich and golden beer. Although we can brew complex beers with the best of them, we never forget that there’s beauty in simplicity.⁠
⁠
Mosaic Promise is now available in 6-pack cans in our taprooms, and it’ll be on draft in our taprooms mid-September. The rest of Michigan will see it in 6-pack cans and on draft in the next few weeks. Head to the link in our bio for more info! #foundersbrewing
